Package: trajSurvR
Type: Package
Title: Longitudinal Trajectory and Survival Analysis for Proteomic Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Ximing", "Ran", email = "ranxm2@users.noreply.github.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions for longitudinal proteomic analysis workflows,
    including quality control, differential expression via mixed-effects models,
    correlation study, GAM/GAMM trajectory modeling, time-to-event analysis
    (baseline Cox, LASSO Cox, time-dependent Cox), event prediction with
    logistic regression, onset-time prediction, and forward greedy or LASSO
    feature selection. A built-in simulation function and plotting helpers
    support rapid prototyping and reporting.
